Talents.Description:
When {LINK#N11250001}<color=#FFD780FF>Gravity Interference</color>{/LINK} is triggered, 4 Elemental Energy will be restored to Columbina;
Additionally, if the Lunar reaction type that accumulates the most <color=#FFD780FF>Gravity</color> for Columbina is Lunar-Charged, Lunar-Bloom, or Lunar-Crystallize, the Lunar Reaction DMG dealt by this instance of Gravity Interference is increased by 12.5%/2.5%/12.5% of Columbina's Max HP respectively. This effect can be triggered at most once every 15s.

All nearby party members' Lunar Reaction DMG is {LINK#N11190007}<color=#FFD780FF>elevated</color>{/LINK} by 1.5%.
